{"tid":973699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本理光公司　計劃將影印機生產　移出中國","createTime":"2019-01-08T10:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T12:59:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9675fbb599864ca9e9912644b22c1e803d319f","tid":973699,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-gy-japanese-company-ricoh-to-move-factory-out-of-china-20190106-ry/4730741.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcantonese-gy-japanese-company-ricoh-to-move-factory-out-of-china-20190106-ry%2F4730741.html&d=VdyLyaYSosf806FHw4nY1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=511d507f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-gy-japanese-company-ricoh-to-move-factory-out-of-china-20190106-ry/4730741.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/B81553F0-DA62-4A30-8489-18CC5DB7378F_cx21_cy17_cw54_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FB81553F0-DA62-4A30-8489-18CC5DB7378F_cx21_cy17_cw54_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=d61a304e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多商業公司感受美中貿易戰壓力之際，一家日本公司準備將一條生產線從中國轉移到泰國，以便減少美中貿易戰對中國出口環境的影響。<br />\n<br />\n生產辦公設備的日本理光公司(Ricoh﹐又譯麗確公司)星期六宣佈，該公司正在準備把在中國的影印機生產遷移到泰國。<br />\n<br />\n理光公司目前把在中國上海和深圳生產的影印機出口到美國。共同社的報導說，理光公司如果最後決定轉移生產，最快能在2個月後從泰國向美國出口產品。報導還說，製造影印機的零部件可能也從中國以外的地區採購。<br />\n<br />\n理光公司的行政總裁接受共同社採訪時表示，預計美中貿易糾紛將長期化，進一步關稅上調將對公司造成很大打擊。<br />\n<br />\n理光公司去年7月宣佈，在中國廣東東莞投資逾百億日元建立新工廠， &ldquo;理光製造(中國)有限公司&rdquo;（Ricoh Manufacturing (China) Ltd.），生產辦公設備。這項計劃的實施狀況目前不得而知。"},{"pid":"8910bbe95b1207c43fcadd2cb2a0cb5e25ddc0a8","tid":973699,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"又贏， 成功將渣取支那人勞動成果的小鬼趕跑"},{"pid":"50a11972e81951deeda136b9305e07629124d730","tid":973699,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"輸左間廠，贏多間廠"},{"pid":"a4cfdad931face289596001953b592c66bb219eb","tid":973699,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n趕走日本仔<br />\n<br />\n中日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}